general.gigTitle: develop a life coaching, consulting, speaker, and trainer website

sellerCard.description: Hello, I am Atika Aslam. I have done Bachelors in Computer Science. With my passion in web development and SEO, I am here to serve Fiverr's great community. You will get perfect quality work beyond your expectations :) Lets get Started!

description.content:
Hello!


I am Atika. I am here to design and develop a life coaching website, consulting, speaker, and trainer website for you.


Are you looking for a standout website for your business? I am here to provide top-notch service with an attractive layout. You will get unbelievably perfect, beautiful, professional coaching and fitness web.


If you are a life coach, mental health coach, fitness trainer, a motivational speaker and want the best web site to present your services globally then you are at the right gig. you will get not only a website, but it will be 100% responsive, user friendly and mobile friendly.


what you will get more:


  • theme-based or custom layout website
  • WordPress conversion into android and IOS app (optional with $75 gig extras)
  • social media, contact form
  • landing page
  • blog page creation
  • subscription option

and many more...


Don't look anywhere just contact me and Let's discuss the project :)


Best Regard

Atika

reviews.comment: It was a real pleasure working with Atika. She patiently explained how a web landing page is assembled, and took in all my explanations and wishes for the different elements. Further changes and amendments led to a final product that I am really happy with.
My website updates were done with excellence! The communication was great and the professionalism was top notch. I will definitely be back for more web work!

Atika did a great job with this. Everything was done according to specification and was delivered a day ahead of schedule which was nice. I've worked with Fiverr talent before and have almost always had to extend the project time. 

I will work with Atika again for sure.
